  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, whisk together garlic powder, soy sauce, sesame oil, and rice vinegar.",
    "Heat a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat. Add half of the whisked mixture to the pan.",
    "Add cherry tomatoes, red bell peppers, and snap peas. Stir-fry for about 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the remaining whisked mixture. Cook for another 1 minute until well combined and heated through.",
    "Garnish with green onions before serving."
